Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.model

package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.model
Miscellaneous model classes for spalloc. Note that many of these are used to drive the creation of Spring MVC-based pages, and so need to be Java Beans.
